<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_246" id="123r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_246_r1l11"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Roſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_246_r1l12"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hanns als wır nehſt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıener <expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l13"><expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> geſchıkt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅch ʒu <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . den ʒınſe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l14">der vns nach vnſers brıefs lawt vnd ſag auf ſand Mıchelſtag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l15"><expan>nehſtuergang<ex>en</ex></expan> / von eẅch <expan>verfall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd noch niht becʒalt ıſt . Alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l16"><expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ . daʒ Jr vns <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ʒinſe . noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l17"><expan>vnuercʒogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> auſrıchtet vnd becʒalet vnd kein <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒıehen</expan> mer daran </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l18">tut . das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır allcʒeıt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vmb eẅch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> . VVan beſchech </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l19">des niht . ſölten wır denn <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>bürg<ex>en</ex></expan> . nach des <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> brıefs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l20">ſag <expan>ʒuſprech<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd manen . das teten wır wıder eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> niht <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l21">ſo <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır des doch niht <expan>v̈berhabe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> poſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l22"><expan>Kath<ex>er</ex>ıne</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_246" id="123r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hanns, als wir nehst
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> geschikt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch zu <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den
                        zinse, der uns nach unsers briefs lawt und sag auf <app><note><q type="date">sand Michelstag
                            <expan>nehstvergang<ex>en</ex></expan></q>29.09.1415</note></app> von ewch
                                <expan>verfall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und noch niht beczalt ist, also
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, daz ir uns
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> zinse noch
                                <expan>unverczogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ausrichtet und beczalet und
                        kein <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cziehen</expan> mer daran tut. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir allczeit
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> umb ewch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>.
                        Wan beschech des niht, sölten wir denn <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bürg<ex>en</ex></expan> nach des <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> briefs sag <expan>zusprech<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und manen, das teten wir wider ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> niht
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, so <expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        des doch niht <expan>überhabe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi> post
                                <expan>Kath<ex>er</ex>ine.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
